{"tid":1488742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"總覺得成個運動偏離左，搞裸跑會唔會好易有位比人插？","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T18:02:58.000Z","uid":308112,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ca565f168ac7e0cf399aee63c848219956e745","tid":1488742,"uid":308112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"Sorry for P牌<br />\n<br />\n首先佩服一下裸跑嗰個肯岀嚟已經好勇，對住咁多人心理壓力一定好大，不如放過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入正題先，我地抗爭緊㗎喎，而家個風氣偏到去好似派膠咁，而且總有預感咁樣會令到成場運動比人一個唔好嘅印象，唔能夠將呢場運動成功嘅機會推到最大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">純粹個人意見，有少少不詳預感，如果有咩得罪希望各位可以體諒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be72506e508770598d7492a0cc5e1745573a8dc","tid":1488742,"uid":255979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"其實本來冇問題，不過現場叫口號就真係俾位人入喇"},{"pid":"9a4be22462ec0ace9f56ef1695ab7bef387366f4","tid":1488742,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:20:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁又不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係咁不安就去做正經野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0346f0bba1011ad27e3acb1b3455572e2bef965","tid":1488742,"uid":308112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4be22462ec0ace9f56ef1695ab7bef387366f4","tid":1488742,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:20:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁又不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係咁不安就去做正經野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:02:58.000Z","msg":"屌斯文啲講都要比人屌鳩洗唔洗咁啊，警剔姐屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}